      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Commander, I think... I understand what I have to do now.",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Up until now, I've always been trapped by my memories of the past, afraid of opening old wounds.",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "I've decided that I won't run from my past anymore...",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "But I can't do that as I am now.",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Le Triomphant made a fist, gentle but filled with determination.",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "As Forbin said, I can't just keep my emotions bottled up.",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "No matter what it takes, I have to make my sisters understand my feelings.",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Perhaps my sisters would get angry at me, but even then...",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "options": [
        {
          "content": "Offer Le Triomphant your support",
          "flag": 1
        }
      ],
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "I... I want to get along with my sisters again!",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Thank you so much, Commander. This is only possible because of you...",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "I won't get jealous of others anymore... because surely, I'll be able to have fun with my own sisters again.",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "options": [
        {
          "content": "You are still cute, though, even if you do decide to run.",
          "flag": 1
        }
      ],
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "From now on, I won't run away from what needs to be done. As my name suggests, I'll be triumphant in reforging my relationship with my sisters!",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Upon hearing my words, Le Triomphant turned a deep shade of red.",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "options": [
        {
          "content": "It's true. You're really cute.",
          "flag": 1
        }
      ],
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Wh-what are you saying? C-calling me c-cute...",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Uuu... F-fine... Then, the next time I'm worried about something, you'd better be there to hear me out...",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "actor": 801010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Since you're the person I trust the most, you won't mind if I rely on you a bit more, right?",
      "blackBg": true,
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    }
